OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA changeable unsettled day with
OL,6,Fsome showers, heaviest at first across
OL,7,FKintyre and Ayrshire, but these
OL,8,Fclearing north towards the Central
OL,9,FBelt while easing, with Ayrshire
OL,10,Fhaving a drier afternoon. A few sunny
OL,11,Fintervals around too.
OL,12,
OL,13,CTonight:FIt will remain mostly cloudy
OL,14,Fthis evening and tonight with a few
OL,15,Fshowers, and just one or two clear
OL,16,Fintervals.
OL,17,
OL,18,CWednesday:FA mostly cloudy day. Mainly
OL,19,Fdry morning with just a few light
OL,20,Fshowers, then some more persistent
OL,21,Frain followed by heavy showers later.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
