OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,6,FRather cloudy with some showers on
OL,7,FThursday and early Friday. Brighter
OL,8,Fthereafter with sunny intervals and
OL,9,Fmore scattered showers.
